      "path": "/Users/venky/Documents/Codex/2026-04-19-build-me-a-trusted-search-using/sample_sources/architecture/trusted_search_starter_kit_notes.md",
      "title": "Starter Kit Notes",
      "acl_groups": [
        "employees"
      ],
      "chunk_index": 0,
      "start_line": 1,
      "end_line": 10,
      "text": "# Starter Kit Notes\n\nThis local project is inspired by a trusted search starter kit that separates ingestion from the API surface.\n\nKey ideas adapted here:\n- keep a connector-style ingestion entrypoint that builds the indexes from source files\n- expose a simple API boundary for search requests\n- combine lexical and vector retrieval\n- preserve citations and confidence metadata in the response\n- leave room for future auth and audit logging upgrades"
    },
